title: Microsoft Windows (10) Technical Preview Pro-Ent build 9879
description:
These are the downloaded versions of Windows (10) Technical Preview.
For build 9879 The pro versions only have an esd, and the
Enterprise versions have a full wim-based ISO.

In the interest of saving everyone's bandwidth, I've created
sfx delta patches from the en-US iso enterprise versions to the
alternate language counterparts. These cannot be applied to the
esd files because of the lzms compression and encryption.

Hash txt files are included.

Instructions for non-en-US exe files:
1 - Double-click the desired file
2 - Wait until it's finished applying the delta to create the new iso.

Instructions for ESD files:
1 - Extract the 4f or wimlib script to the folder containing the esd files.
2 - Run admin command prompt and navigate to the esd files' folder.
3 - Run "decrypt filename.esd" ***
*** Replace with actual full esd filname. Pro-Tip: Highlight filename
and then use ctrl-c, then right click on command prompt window and
select the paste option.
